  Firm Overview 


Frank V. Lawson Jr. and Kenneth W. Kroeker founded Lawson Kroeker Investment
Management in 1986.
 
Lawson Kroeker is an independent investment advisory firm located in Omaha, Nebraska.
 
We are long-term investors who buy high quality companies with very good growth potential at discount prices.
 
We believe that preservation of capital is as important as growth of capital.
 
Lawson Kroeker manages separate individual and institutional portfolios.
 
We have investors throughout the U.S.

















